title: Pritzker says Trump ordering Texas National Guard troops to Illinois and Oregon

author: Sally Pipes
description: Is it worth shutting down the government to keep billions in federal cash flowing to health insurers? That’s a question Republicans should be asking Democrats every chance they get.  The minority party has brought business in Washington to a halt as part of a wrongheaded strategy to obscure the out-of-control growth in health insurance costs […]
title: Shut down the enhanced Obamacare subsidies, not the government
